==Description==

The [[FreeGrid_StorageBox|FreeGrid StorageBox]] tool creates a storage box.

This tool is part of the [[FreeGrid_Workbench|FreeGrid Workbench]], an [[External_workbenches|external workbench]] that can be installed with the [[Image:Std_AddonMgr.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]].

==Usage==

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:FreeGrid_StorageBox.svg|16px]] [[FreeGrid_StorageBox|Storage box]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|FreeGrid → [[Image:FreeGrid_StorageBox.svg|16px]] Storage box}} option from the menu.
# A storage box is created with properties based on the current preferences.
# Optionally select the object and change its properties in the [[Property_editor|Property editor]].

==Properties==

A FreeGrid StorageBox object is derived from a [[Part_Feature|Part Feature]] object and inherits all its properties. It also has the following additional properties:

=== Data ===

{{Properties_Title|Box features}}

* {{PropertyData|BoxGrip|Bool}}: Default is {{value|True}}. Add grip/label area at rear of box.
* {{PropertyData|BoxGripDepth|Length}}: Default is {{value|15mm}}. Depth of grip (mm).
* {{PropertyData|BoxOpenFront|Bool}}: Default is {{value|False}}. Leave front of box open.
* {{PropertyData|BoxRamp|Bool}}: Default is {{value|True}}. Add scoop inside front of box.
* {{PropertyData|FloorSupport|Bool}}: Default is {{value|True}}. Add integral floor support.

{{Properties_Title|Internal divisions}}

* {{PropertyData|DivisionHeight|Percent}}: Default is {{value|100}}. Height of internal divisions relative to the box.
* {{PropertyData|DivisionsX|IntegerConstraint}}: Default is {{value|1}}. Number of divisions along the X axis.
* {{PropertyData|DivisionsY|IntegerConstraint}}: Default is {{value|1}}. Number of divisions along the Y axis.

{{Properties_Title|Magnet mount}}

* {{PropertyData|MagnetDiameter|Length}}: Default is {{value|6mm}}. Diameter of the magnet.
* {{PropertyData|MagnetHeight|Length}}: Default is {{value|2mm}}. Height of the magnet.

{{Properties_Title|Position on grid}}

* {{PropertyData|PositionX|IntegerConstraint}}: Default is {{value|0}}. Box position on the grid in the X axis. Starts at zero.
* {{PropertyData|PositionY|IntegerConstraint}}: Default is {{value|0}}. Box position on the grid in the Y axis. Starts at zero.

{{Properties_Title|Size}}

* {{PropertyData|Depth|IntegerConstraint}}: Default is {{value|1}}. Number of 50[mm] units in Y direction.
* {{PropertyData|Height|Length}}: Default is {{value|1}}. Height (in Z direction), enter value and unit example: 4cm, 1dm, 3in, 0.5ft.
* {{PropertyData|Width|IntegerConstraint}}: Default is {{value|50mm}}. Number of 50[mm] units in X direction.


